ing: 1 (10 ounce) can diced tomatoes with green chile peppers, with liquid
1/2 (1 ounce) package dry ranch salad dressing mix
1 (6 ounce) can sliced black olives, drained
n: Cheesy Sour Cream and Salsa Dip
des: "This creamy chip dip is different from any I've ever had.  Mix sour cream with tomatoes and green chilies, black olives and Cheddar cheese. Always a hit at parties. Great texture and taste! Serve with tortilla chips or crackers."
ins: Mix together sour cream, canned tomatoes, dry ranch dressing mix, black olives, and shredded cheese. Chill for 2 hours before serving.
